summary: Commissions to Pay for Medical Bills Hey friends. If you've ever considered commissioning me, now would be a lovely time to do...
caption:
Commissions to Pay for Medical Bills


Hey friends. If you’ve ever considered commissioning me, now would be a lovely time to do so!

I’m staring down some hefty medical bills due to a mass I’m getting removed (the doctors tell me it’s most likely benign, and non cancerous, but the original core biopsy was inconclusive, so better safe than sorry), and am looking to utilize all of my skill sets to help cover the cost. I’ve already paid the $3200 for the original core biopsy, but that wiped out my savings, and I’ve still got the surgical biopsy to go. That is going to run me somewhere around $6500 (hopefully less, because I’ll hit my deductible with this procedure, but there’s no way to tell until I get the actual bill), which is what commission money will be going to.

Lots of you know my art: I’m game to draw just about anything, work in both digital and traditional media, and can even do some design work or animation for you as well. Line art is just $10, $20 for a full color bust, and $30+ for full body work/other ideas you’d like to discuss (check out my website if you’d like more examples). Alternatively, you can back my Patreon and get some of the above each month for your contribution. Everything I earn will be going towards paying these bills off, so let me make art for you in the meantime.

Feel free to share, or email me at sarah.lokay@gmail.com if you’ve got questions. One day I hope our healthcare system won’t do this to people, but in the meantime, thanks for reading.
